<P>THOUGHTS AND SENTIMENTS ON THE EVIL AND WICKED TRAFFIC OF THE SLAVERY AND COMMERCE OF THE HUMAN SPECIES, HUMBLY SUBMITTED TO The INHABITANTS of <HI>GREAT-BRITAIN,</HI> BY OTTOBAH CUGOANO, A NATIVE of <HI>AFRICA.</HI></P>
